p/e rasyosu çok aldatıcı olabilir, illa değerleme metriği arıyorsanız ev ve ebitda çarpanlarına yönelin.


    Understand the company
    Operations
    Business model
    Company's competitors/rivals
    Company's debt and compare it with rivals.
    Company’s prospects

    Company’s structure and revenue
    Company’s profits over the years
    Revenue growth over the years
    Company’s debt
    Corporate governance
    Rate of turnover


